      • ManualLocationText

        public ManualLocationText(Context c,
                  Activity a)
        Assuming that the user typed something in the text field, once they press the search/ok button on their keyboard we get whatever the user wrote and pass it on to ManualLocationHandler to be converted to latitude and longitude. Else, the user will be informed by a toast notification that the text box is empty.
